data.description: Welcome to this absolutely stunning townhome nestled in the highly sought-after Edgewood neighborhood of Atlanta. Prepare to be captivated by the perfect blend of luxury, convenience, and style that awaits you within these walls.      Centrally located, this end unit puts you in the heart of Atlanta's most vibrant and trendy hotspots. Imagine strolling through the eclectic streets of Kirkwood, exploring the unique shops of East Atlanta Village, or immersing yourself in the vibrant energy of Little Five Points. With endless possibilities at your doorstep, you'll be living in the heart of Atlanta's "it" scene.    But the excitement doesn't stop there. Step outside your front door and be greeted by The Trolley Trail, a gateway to the renowned Beltline. Imagine the adventures that await as you traverse this expansive network of paths, meandering through picturesque parks and discovering hidden gems along the way. And just across the street lies Walker Park, offering a serene escape from the bustling city with its open fields, playground, and dog park.    As you step inside, prepare to be dazzled by the meticulous attention to detail and luxurious finishes that adorn every inch of this home. From the gleaming waterproof hardwood flooring to the custom mahogany cabinets and premium granite countertops, no expense has been spared in creating a space that exudes elegance and sophistication. Entertain with ease in the open floor plan, where the living room invites you to relax with the inlay speaker system, large leather sofa, and immersive television along with the chef-inspired kitchen that will beckon you to create culinary masterpieces.    The bedrooms offer a haven of tranquility, each boasting its own private bathroom and ample closet space. Indulge in the spa-like oasis of the master bathroom, where the heated tile floors along with a complete floor-to-ceiling tile enclosure, 3 custom inlays, and a selection of shower options await. The framed mirrors, custom lighting, and premium granite countertops are sure to transform your daily routine into a blissful retreat.    But this home isn't just about luxury - it's about convenience and technology too. The smart home features allow you to effortlessly control every aspect of your living space; lighting, fans, security, televisions, temperature, and bedding all with the command of your voice. And with no rental restrictions in the HOA, the potential for investment income is limitless.    The seller is highly motivated and is entertaining all offers, including owner financing options. Don't miss your chance to experience the excitement and allure of this extraordinary townhome. Schedule your private tour today and unlock the door to a world of endless possibilities in one of Atlanta's hottest real estate markets.
